<item>
            <title>[SPARK-24781] Using a reference from Dataset in Filter/Sort might not work.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-24781</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we use a reference from&#160;&lt;tt&gt;Dataset&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;filter&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;sort&lt;/tt&gt;, which was not used in the prior &lt;tt&gt;select&lt;/tt&gt;, an &lt;tt&gt;AnalysisException&lt;/tt&gt; occurs, e.g.,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-scala&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; df = Seq((&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, 0), (&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, 1)).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;name&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
df.select(df(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;name&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)).filter(df(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) === 0).show()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;org.apache.spark.sql.AnalysisException: Resolved attribute(s) id#6 missing from name#5 in operator !Filter (id#6 = 0).;;
!Filter (id#6 = 0)
   +- AnalysisBarrier
      +- Project [name#5]
         +- Project [_1#2 AS name#5, _2#3 AS id#6]
            +- LocalRelation [_1#2, _2#3]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If we use &lt;tt&gt;col&lt;/tt&gt; instead, it works:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-scala&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; df = Seq((&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, 0), (&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, 1)).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;name&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
df.select(col(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;name&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)).filter(col(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) === 0).show()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
